%% ABOUTME: Validation pipeline — blocking and advisory checks run in parallel; fail paths branch to the side; advisory findings feed the polish pass
flowchart TD
    IN["Instrumented output"]
    G["`Blocking structural gate checks
*Syntax · Elision · Lint · Weaver static check*`"]
    J(( ))
    B["`Blocking quality checks
*Schema fidelity · Coverage · Code quality
API-only · LLM judge (if new names)*`"]
    A["`Non-blocking advisory gate checks
*No Utility Spans · Async Operation Spans
Attribute Data Quality · etc.*`"]
    GFAIL(["Structural fail — file rejected"])
    SFAIL(["Fail — findings returned
blocking failures + advisory"])
    AGENT["Agent: one improvement pass
(passing file + advisory findings)"]
    RECHECK["Full validation re-run"]
    IMPROVED(["Improved file committed"])
    PRIOR(["Prior passing file committed"])

    IN --> G
    G -->|all pass| J
    G -->|any fail| GFAIL
    J --> B
    J --> A
    B -->|any fail| SFAIL
    B -->|"all pass — passing file"| AGENT
    A -->|advisory findings| AGENT
    AGENT --> RECHECK
    RECHECK -->|all blocking checks pass| IMPROVED
    RECHECK -->|any blocking checks fail| PRIOR

